   $lim_(x->0^-)(2x + |x|)/(4x - 3|x|) = lim_(x->0^-)(2x - x)/(4x + 3x) = lim_(x->0^-)(x)/(7x) = lim_(x->0^-)1/7 = 1/7$
   
